title: Mars Phobos - Bootleg Pack 1
description:
Thanks so much for downloading my music, it means a lot to me.
I am "Mars Phobos" (stupid name) and I hope you enjoy at least some of what I've made here.
This is my first bootleg pack, I generally make all the music from scratch and solely use the vocals from other tracks.

You can support me onand

Thanks again, enjoy!

-MP
